# Rural Blood Bank – AI Context File
# This file helps AI assistants understand the project quickly and reduce token usage.
# Last updated: 2026-03-08

## Identity
- **Name**: Rural Blood Bank
- **Repo**: 3s-Soft/bloodbank
- **Purpose**: Community-powered, multi-tenant blood donation platform for rural Bangladesh
- **Version**: 0.1.0

## Tech Stack
| Layer          | Technology                                    |
|----------------|-----------------------------------------------|
| Framework      | Next.js 16.1.5 (App Router, Turbopack)        |
| Language       | TypeScript 5.x (strict mode)                  |
| Database       | MongoDB via Mongoose 9                         |
| Auth           | NextAuth.js 4 (JWT strategy, Credentials + Firebase Google) |
| Styling        | Tailwind CSS 4 (PostCSS plugin)                |
| Forms          | React Hook Form + Zod 4 validation            |
| Notifications  | Sonner (toasts), Web Push API (push notifs)    |
| Icons          | Lucide React                                   |
| PWA            | @ducanh2912/next-pwa                           |
| i18n           | Custom (English + Bangla), context-based       |
| Containerization | Docker + docker-compose                      |

## Path Aliases
- `@/*` → project root (e.g., `@/lib/db/mongodb`, `@/components/ui/button`)

## Project Structure (Key Directories)
```
bloodbank/
├── app/
│   ├── (auth)/                 # Auth route group
│   ├── (dashboard)/            # Dashboard route group
│   ├── [orgSlug]/              # Multi-tenant org pages (dynamic route)
